section.def:
committee
                (委員會) means a committee of the Council
            established under section 9;

paragraph.content:
at least one but not more than 3 public officers appointed by the Chief Executive;
                    (Amended 53 of 2000 s.
                            3)

subparagraph.content:
at least 5 shall be persons considered by the Chief Executive to have
                        had relevant experience in commerce, industry or a profession in Hong
                        Kong;

not more than 3 shall be persons considered by the Chief Executive to
                        have had relevant experience in education, other than higher education,
                        either in Hong Kong or elsewhere;

paragraph.content:
the appointment or dismissal of the President or a Vice President;
                    (Amended 23 of 2002 s.
                            48)
